Chart/Plot/Annotated version 0.01
=================================

No system dependencies for this module, assuming you have its base
class Chart::Plot installed and working. This will require you to have
GD as well, so deal with that first.

This module is pure Perl, so no XS headaches here either.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Chart::Plot        0.10
  GD                 1.27
  Class::MethodMaker 1.02

